WEBVTT

00:03:57.978 --> 00:04:00.963
Tule sredinski potnik spet kihne,

00:04:00.987 --> 00:04:03.700
a tokrat lahko zrak potisnemo navzdol

00:04:03.724 --> 00:04:06.437
do filtrov za izhod.

00:04:06.461 --> 00:04:07.857
Enako velja s strani,

00:04:07.881 --> 00:04:11.110
vidite, kako patogene potisnemo navzdol.

00:04:11.682 --> 00:04:15.176
Poglejmo isti scenarij

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:16.889
z vstavljeno inovacijo,

00:04:16.913 --> 00:04:18.929
ko sredinski potnik kihne,

00:04:18.953 --> 00:04:22.026
gre zrak naravnost do izhoda

00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:25.771
in nima časa okužiti drugih.

00:04:25.795 --> 00:04:28.919
Potnika poleg osebe v sredini

00:04:28.943 --> 00:04:31.176
ne vdihujeta praktično nobenih patogenov.